{
  "stem": "21978.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there were bunks made like square, like a bed, which I don't know if-- you know what bunks are.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's three layers bunks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people were lying on bottom bunks, middle, and top.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were no mattresses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know if we had some kind of a straw or something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I really don't-- I think it was just plain timber that the we-- wood that we were lying on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the middle of the whole building, or whole the barrack, there was like a chimney.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a-- a-- it went through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was-- you could sit on it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was cement, kind of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like a table or whatever, which went through the whole building.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And on one side, there was a fire going like a oven or stove where eventually, you might have warmed up something if you have stolen-- if you were lucky enough to get couple of potatoes or something.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Or you have your bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you might have been able to toast it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I can't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the whole building was just the middle where there was this-- we called it chimney-- come in, come in, like a stove.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't really know, can't describe it-- and the bunks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And in the front of it, there was a separated little room, which was for the blockalteste-- that was the prisoner who was in charge of the block.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She was the one who got-- who made sure that everything was in order, it was clean as much as it was possible, that people were coming at 4 o'clock in the morning for there was wake-up.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
